;
; PuzzleBOBS configuration file
;-------------------------------
;
; Here you can configure PuzzleBOBS game. If you find a value in which is specified the range
; between brackets you must respect its and consider that extremes values could be included.
; If you don't find range you could insert a SIGNED LONG INT value from -2147483647
; to +2147483647. If you find (+) you must insert a >0 value. 
; If you insert a string respect Amiga Dos directives and use quotes in strings with spaces.
; If an error occurs, PuzzleBOBS will confirm it to you. 
;
; Have a good configuration.
;
;
; ----------------
; ConfigFile About
; ----------------
;
; Here there is a block of string about ConfigFile's author. Each string can not go over 79 chars of lenght.
;
"VIC E BABES"		
"Countries represented by bobs in this set are:"		
"Canada, France, Germany, Italy, Romania, Spain"		
"United Kingdom and United States of America."		
